version_description:
New photo effects from this update will literally knock you down! :)

Amazing Half-Robot Face Mask, gorgeous Alien Transformation and blasting Head Explosion effect!

Star Wars fans, rejoice, because we've added Darth Vader and Yoda face montage templates.

Girls, try on a foxy Christmas Girl costume: just choose your selfie photo and get a cool profile picture.

Here we go with new animal photo effects! Ever wanted to be as strong as a gorilla or as lazy as a cat? Try it in a click!
For romantic souls we now have photo templates with ape and feline couples: add your and your sweetheart's face to them.

- New effects are HERE! We hope you'll like them all ;)
- We've made the app a little bit more convenient
- Minor bug fixes & visual improvements are also included
